@startuml
title Hình 2.6 - Trusted Subsystem Pattern với Keycloak và API Gateway

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam ArrowColor #475569
skinparam ArrowThickness 1.3
skinparam ParticipantBorderColor #475569
skinparam ParticipantBackgroundColor #F1F5F9
skinparam NoteBorderColor #F97316
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #FFF7ED

actor "User" as User
participant "Storefront /\nAdmin Panel" as Client #E0F2FE
participant "Keycloak\nAuthorization Server" as Keycloak #FEF3C7
participant "API Gateway\nResource Server" as Gateway #DCFCE7
box "Docker internal network\nBackend services không expose ra ngoài" #ECFDF5
participant "order-service" as OrderService #BBF7D0
participant "product-service" as ProductService #BBF7D0
participant "user-service" as UserService #BBF7D0
end box

User -> Client : Đăng nhập
Client -> Keycloak : Authorization Code Flow / token request
Keycloak --> Client : Access Token JWT\nRS256 signed

Client -> Gateway : API request\nAuthorization: Bearer JWT
Gateway -> Keycloak : Lấy public key / JWKS\nhoặc dùng cache
Gateway -> Gateway : Verify signature,\nissuer, audience, expiry, roles

alt JWT hợp lệ
  Gateway -> OrderService : Forward request\nX-User-Id\nX-User-Roles\nX-User-Email
  OrderService -> OrderService : Tin tưởng header\nvì chỉ Gateway gọi được
  OrderService --> Gateway : Business response
  Gateway --> Client : Response
else JWT sai hoặc hết hạn
  Gateway --> Client : 401 / 403
end

note over OrderService,UserService
  Backend services không tự xác minh JWT.
  Điều kiện bắt buộc: chỉ API Gateway
  được truy cập trực tiếp vào mạng nội bộ.
end note

@enduml
